on the due date, the ceremony has to be stalled again.\n\nThe reconstructed Balgopaleshwor Temple has got few changes. The temple formerly constructed in Granthakut or Shikar Style was changed to Gumbaz style after the earthquake of 1934.\n\nThe temple has regained its former style Shikhar after the earthquake of 2015.","title":"Balgopaleshwor Temple of Ranipokhari to get spire on Thursday - Khabarhub","url":"http://english.khabarhub.com/2020/29/131113/","video":[]}
